headline: Welltower price target lowered to $140 from $143 at Wells Fargo
summary: Wells Fargo lowered the firm’s price target on Welltower (WELL) to $140 from $143 and keeps an Equal Weight rating on the shares. The firm is adjusting price targets across its Healthcare and Net Leasing REIT coverage based on its AFFO yield spread regression analyses and updated NAVs.
